        "kind": "pull_request",
        "title": "feat(raft): add CLI wake bridge channel",
        "body": "## What Problem This Solves\n\nOpenClaw users cannot currently connect an agent to Raft's local CLI bridge. Raft can notify a local process that messages are pending, but there is no supported OpenClaw channel to route that wake signal to an agent.\n\n## Why This Change Was Made\n\nAdds Raft as an official external channel plugin. The plugin starts Raft's local `agent bridge`, accepts only authenticated content-free wake hints on loopback, persists replay protection in the plugin state database, and dispatches a serial agent turn that directs the agent to read and respond through the Raft CLI. It intentionally does not treat Raft wake payloads as message content or implement a synthetic outbound transport.\n\n## User Impact\n\nOperators can configure a Raft profile through `channels.raft`, start the gateway, and have an OpenClaw agent wake when Raft has pending work. Multiple named accounts are supported, as are environment-backed default profiles.\n\n## Evidence\n\n- `node scripts/run-vitest.mjs extensions/raft/src/accounts.test.ts extensions/raft/src/channel.test.ts extensions/raft/src/gateway.test.ts test/official-channel-catalog.test.ts test/plugin-npm-package-manifest.test.ts src/config/validation.channel-metadata.test.ts src/plugins/manifest-registry.test.ts`\n  - 118 tests passed across four Vitest shards on the rebased head.\n- `node scripts/generate-plugin-inventory-doc.mjs --check`\n- `node --import tsx scripts/generate-bundled-channel-config-metadata.ts --check`\n- `node scripts/generate-npm-shrinkwrap.mjs --check --package-dir extensions/raft`\n- `node scripts/report-test-temp-creations.mjs --base origin/main --head HEAD --fail-on-findings`\n- `git diff --check origin/main...HEAD`\n- Fresh `autoreview --mode local --engine codex`: clean, no accepted/actionable findings.\n- `OPENCLAW_CHECK_CHANGED_REMOTE_CHILD=1 OPENCLAW_CHANGED_LANES_RAW_SYNC=1 corepack pnpm check:changed` passed in Blacksmith Testbox `tbx_01kvmcqcmwpbgk6wy1shfcry3b`.\n- `corepack pnpm build` passed in the same Testbox before the type/test-only follow-up commit.\n- The Crabbox coordinator returned `HTTP 500` (`error code: 1101`), so the Testbox result is the remote changed-gate proof.\n- The local `raft` CLI and a Raft account were not available, so this PR does not claim live bridge delivery proof.\n",
